          "value": "<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> @Check[type:fortitude|dc:20]</p>\n<p><strong>Maximum Duration</strong> 1 hour</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Slowed]{Slowed 1} (1 round)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Slowed]{Slowed 2} (1 minute)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Unconscious]{Unconscious} with no check to wake up (1 round)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 4</strong> unconscious with no perception check to wake up (1 hour).</p>"
